{"3863000": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Angel's love", "steam_appid": 3863000, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>如果你也能看看我的其他遊戲，我會很高興。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/01c377c337b50f4d6764052c7a805762.avif?t=1769536920\" width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安琪兒把自己的一切都奉獻給了夢想成為超級巨星的男友。她打三份工，為他提供舒適的生活，而他則靠著她的錢練習並參加無數試鏡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/c0f632c240e19c51e3b2bec948d62f5a.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >致命的診斷和愛人的背叛在同一天發生。人生結束了。還是沒有？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/27122229a3549b9d737cfa5f98537abf.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/a95704c2d8dd5ace98274abe59059924.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果這個世界上有一個生物，能讓安琪兒恢復健康，還能幫她報復那個自私的背叛者呢？太棒了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但有一個問題……這個生物是一個淫蕩、渴望性愛（最好是群交）、毒品和非法娛樂的魅魔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/695b6823eb1b9fafc5161f0f475a38cf.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為幫助的報酬，她只要求一件事……對安琪兒身體的控制權！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/8055a1bf7316788b18ec890475a36b97.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但沒有選擇！只能同意，在稍微討價還價後爭取到更好的條件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是：有教養、善良、正直且有原則的安琪兒被迫與一個自私、淫蕩又瘋狂的魅魔共用身體。這個魅魔還能改變自己的身體，甚至是安琪兒的身體……各種方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/7d38230729dbd295663651e301c476ac.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.poster.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.webm?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.mp4?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次魅魔控制身體的時期，對安琪兒來說都會帶來不愉快的驚喜、麻煩，甚至災難。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/659dfe9a4d08b3da346a7d6aea977613.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不過，安琪兒也不是省油的燈！她懂得保護自己，必要時甚至會報復。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.poster.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.webm?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.mp4?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何將這種不穩定的生活與安琪兒突然決定成為超級巨星、並在對方最意想不到的領域報復前男友結合起來？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸好，魅魔的一些超自然能力能幫助她在事業路上前進。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/a2f9c94580b23a013ef2ffb1020e43d6.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能和瘋狂的身體室友談判，讓自己的生活步入正軌嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能報復前男友嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能維持與現在同住的親人之間的關係嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還是，在壞影響下，她自己會墮入慾望、墮落和無法自控的低級欲望的深淵？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>決定權在你手中。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Angel's Love》</strong>是一部風格為扶她的情色視覺小說，講述了兩個性格截然相反的人物之間的對抗故事：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過7000張4K解析度的靜態圖片，轉換為Ultra HD以獲得最佳畫質。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過200個動畫性愛場景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7–10小時的遊戲時間。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眾多選擇會影響與其他角色的關係。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情有兩個不同結局，還有許多支線故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些不妨礙單手遊玩的迷你遊戲。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由移動系統——可在場景間自由移動，不會破壞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敘事，還鼓勵探索環境、發現隱藏事件和有趣冒險。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有機會成為超級巨星，從娛樂圈巔峰報復安琪兒的前男友。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量可攻略和不可攻略的女孩……甚至還有男孩。不過，你可以自由選擇與誰、如何互動。嗯……幾乎自由。魅魔對此有自己的看法。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選擇：走天使還是惡魔的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/c45c2aef11a5078530d71facbd58a2c4.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成「魅魔之書」中的情色任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/7d282708af3e9e0760dc84770663f2a3.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解決頑皮魅魔帶來的麻煩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力維持與安琪兒親人的良好關係。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/e2dbc7851f492a44d0072a0604f7659b.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者……把她們帶壞到極致。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/4a8a65866b7bd8bf53604c3508b3e86f.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>決定權在你手中。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>如果你也能看看我的其他遊戲，我會很高興。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/01c377c337b50f4d6764052c7a805762.avif?t=1769536920\" width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安琪兒把自己的一切都奉獻給了夢想成為超級巨星的男友。她打三份工，為他提供舒適的生活，而他則靠著她的錢練習並參加無數試鏡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/c0f632c240e19c51e3b2bec948d62f5a.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >致命的診斷和愛人的背叛在同一天發生。人生結束了。還是沒有？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/27122229a3549b9d737cfa5f98537abf.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/a95704c2d8dd5ace98274abe59059924.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果這個世界上有一個生物，能讓安琪兒恢復健康，還能幫她報復那個自私的背叛者呢？太棒了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但有一個問題……這個生物是一個淫蕩、渴望性愛（最好是群交）、毒品和非法娛樂的魅魔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/695b6823eb1b9fafc5161f0f475a38cf.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為幫助的報酬，她只要求一件事……對安琪兒身體的控制權！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/8055a1bf7316788b18ec890475a36b97.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但沒有選擇！只能同意，在稍微討價還價後爭取到更好的條件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是：有教養、善良、正直且有原則的安琪兒被迫與一個自私、淫蕩又瘋狂的魅魔共用身體。這個魅魔還能改變自己的身體，甚至是安琪兒的身體……各種方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/7d38230729dbd295663651e301c476ac.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.poster.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.webm?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/326984925b49bf17e1fc1d88eb331136.mp4?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次魅魔控制身體的時期，對安琪兒來說都會帶來不愉快的驚喜、麻煩，甚至災難。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/659dfe9a4d08b3da346a7d6aea977613.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不過，安琪兒也不是省油的燈！她懂得保護自己，必要時甚至會報復。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.poster.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.webm?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/446330afd0755d5e972e045d03777d6b.mp4?t=1769536920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何將這種不穩定的生活與安琪兒突然決定成為超級巨星、並在對方最意想不到的領域報復前男友結合起來？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸好，魅魔的一些超自然能力能幫助她在事業路上前進。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/a2f9c94580b23a013ef2ffb1020e43d6.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能和瘋狂的身體室友談判，讓自己的生活步入正軌嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能報復前男友嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能維持與現在同住的親人之間的關係嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還是，在壞影響下，她自己會墮入慾望、墮落和無法自控的低級欲望的深淵？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>決定權在你手中。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Angel's Love》</strong>是一部風格為扶她的情色視覺小說，講述了兩個性格截然相反的人物之間的對抗故事：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過7000張4K解析度的靜態圖片，轉換為Ultra HD以獲得最佳畫質。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過200個動畫性愛場景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7–10小時的遊戲時間。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眾多選擇會影響與其他角色的關係。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情有兩個不同結局，還有許多支線故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些不妨礙單手遊玩的迷你遊戲。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由移動系統——可在場景間自由移動，不會破壞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敘事，還鼓勵探索環境、發現隱藏事件和有趣冒險。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有機會成為超級巨星，從娛樂圈巔峰報復安琪兒的前男友。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量可攻略和不可攻略的女孩……甚至還有男孩。不過，你可以自由選擇與誰、如何互動。嗯……幾乎自由。魅魔對此有自己的看法。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選擇：走天使還是惡魔的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/c45c2aef11a5078530d71facbd58a2c4.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成「魅魔之書」中的情色任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/7d282708af3e9e0760dc84770663f2a3.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解決頑皮魅魔帶來的麻煩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力維持與安琪兒親人的良好關係。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/e2dbc7851f492a44d0072a0604f7659b.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者……把她們帶壞到極致。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/extras/4a8a65866b7bd8bf53604c3508b3e86f.avif?t=1769536920\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>決定權在你手中。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>", "short_description": "《Angel's love》— 一部情色視覺小說。一個身體內兩個靈魂對抗：謙虛有教養的Angel，和入侵她身體的淫蕩好色的魅魔。在這種情況下能否成為流行巨星並向前任復仇呢？", "supported_languages": "英文, 俄文, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 保加利亞文, 匈牙利文, 越南文, 希臘文, 丹麥文, 印尼語, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 繁體中文, 簡體中文, 韓文, 荷蘭文, 挪威文, 波蘭文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 羅馬尼亞文, 泰文, 土耳其文, 烏克蘭文, 芬蘭文, 捷克文, 瑞典文, 日文, 印地語, 菲律賓語", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/44b80532a336afb055b1b6b122dbfe8341a689f3/header.jpg?t=1769536920", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/451ef4cd92abbc45c801b224374afd5ce208095b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1769536920", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3863000/451ef4cd92abbc45c801b224374afd5ce208095b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1769536920", "website": "https://gpoint.zone/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 or higher<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 or DirectX 9.0 compatible<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 8 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 or higher<br></li><li><strong